ComicInfo.Summary:
The Day After Part II: Badrock battles the monstrous Husk through the sewers under his father's lab. Youngblood invites the young, new hero to join their team and Badrock accepts.
From The Same Cloth: The Mossad asks Masada to take out a former friend who is going after an anti-Semitic African American leader.
